# JetBrain

The creators of Kotlin offer an extensive documentation and a free course for Kotlin basics.

## Documentation

[This](https://kotlinlang.org/) is the official homepage for Kotlin.
[Click here](https://kotlinlang.org/docs/home.html) to get to their documentation.
[Here](https://kotlinlang.org/docs/getting-started.html) you'll find their tips on getting started.
They also provide a bunch of [learning materials](https://kotlinlang.org/docs/learning-materials-overview.html).


## Course

As mentioned, [this](https://hyperskill.org/tracks/18) is the free beginner's course created by JetBrains themselves.
It is powered by HyperSkill.
